                </p>
                <p>There is no exportation of any of these products to-the United States, Russia, or
                    British India.</p>
                <p>The excess of importation into Belgium over exportation of rye to France is
                    51,897,606 kilograms; that of peas, beans, &amp;c., from Holland is 7,102,616
                    kilograms. Should legislation of the nature proposed be <pb facs="0126" n="26"
                        xml:id="pg_26"/> enacted, it will doubtless affect the importation of grain
                    from the United States, the value of which is thus given: <table cols="2"
                        rows="8">
                        <row>
                            <cell rendition="#border-top #border-bottom #border-right">Grain.</cell>
                            <cell rendition="#border-top #border-bottom">Value.</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
